## Capo 2nd Fret

The song is normally in E. I want to play it using chords in the family of D.

## Chord Progressions

I'm doing a simple I-IV-V mainly. Not interested in complicating things.

### Verse

    D . . (A) G . A .    (repeat)

### Pre-Chorus

Basically, this:

    G . . . G . . . A . . . A . . .  x2

Not shown here, but you can also may switch between A-G-A-G-A a lot at the very end of that chorus.

### Chorus

    D . . (A) G . A .     (repeat)

