### Other riffs

For the end of the chorus ("Badlands... whoa, whoa whoa whoa...") part, this way of playing the G to A transition will capture the vocal melody.

    E –––2––––––––3–––2–––0––––––––
    B –––3––––––––0–––0–––2–––3––––
    G –––2––––––––0–––0–––2–––2––––
    D –––0––––––––0–––0–––2–––2––––
    A ––––––––––––2–––2–––0–––0––––
    E ––––––––––––3–––3––––––––––––
         D        G       A
